file_content.text: May the Force be with you.
We each walk our own path.
Our current struggles will become armor for the future.
Sith are flawed but working with them has been enlightening.
I've never felt so at peace.
Even the greatest institutions started off as only an idea. In time, we too, will grow.
The more we learn, the more powerful we become.
Sana-Rae has such a unique perspective of the Force. I am honored to learn from her.
The Jedi Order does not have all the answers. It's a humbling and comforting thought.
I have chosen the correct path. I hope others will follow.
